{"tid":203503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★政府加強取締工廈劏房 有團體冀有措施安置劏房戶","createTime":"2017-04-16T10:36:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T13:29:41.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6cfbfa4c208009f474a08c2c51b1a588f6532035","tid":203503,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T10:36:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/58f33d6c6db28cd37e3e3436?lang=cht\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F58f33d6c6db28cd37e3e3436%3Flang%3Dcht&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjYzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=188772af\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/58f33d6c6db28cd37e3e3436?lang=cht</a><br />\n<br />\n樓價高企，而住屋租金亦不斷上升，有市民因而違規租住工廈劏房，但政府基於安全問題，近年加強取締，有劏房戶希望當局有相應安置措施。<br />\n<br />\n這幢工廈全層改建成迷你寫字樓，每個單位有獨立鐵閘，有些出租作貨倉，亦有人當住宅。陳生以1800元租了一個約二百呎單位。於那邊廁所打水後，拿回來煲。<br />\n<br />\n單位內無洗手間、無熱水爐，要洗澡就要到公用洗手間取水，回單位煲熱。更怕被人發現在這裡居住，不敢買床，每日「打地鋪」。<br />\n<br />\n以工廈當住宅的大有人在。陳先生表示：「認識了十幾個都是這樣，還有一個是一家大小，兩夫婦一個女兒，那邊還要四千多元租。」<br />\n<br />\n過去一年全港平均租金升百分之七，不少人「越租越細」，按統計處去年的數字，全港有約8萬8千間住宅「劏房」，有二十萬人居住，多少人住進工廈劏房則沒有統計數字。<br />\n<br />\n過去四年當局巡查了118幢工廈，幾乎全部都有人住，已向業主提出三十宗檢控。陳生之前住的工廈劏房亦由於被政府發現，業主不再出租，但他並無因此而脫離工廈生活。<br />\n<br />\n陳先生說：「最重要是錢，我一個月只有八千元(收入)，如果真的不讓我住，我真的唯一選擇就是露宿街頭。」<br />\n<br />\n有協助劏房戶的團體指沒有安置措施，並不能解決居住工廈問題。葵涌劏房居民大聯盟召集人吳堃廉說：「他們只會由一幢工廈搬到另一幢工廈，整體情況、安全問題等是沒有解決到。 政府會否考慮取締工廈居民會否有安置安排，如考慮改建空置工廈作過渡性房屋。」<br />\n<br />\n為了進一步打擊工廈劏房，政府計劃於本立法年度將工廈經營住宅刑事化建議提交立法會。不過如何安置受影響的居民，屋宇署就回應指，會與房屋署、社會福利署保持聯繫。"},{"pid":"28da6eb83e56ae4bb16348d3a734394e7b503040","tid":203503,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T10:37:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efafa4e6117ff11c2760bcb31bd3f5d1fd211c18","tid":203503,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T10:37:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5fc70ca6e757ad16955afaddea29b768c81cb16","tid":203503,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T10:39:37.000Z","msg":"全港劏房戶湧去林鄭屋企瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d10c1956506272a36277f786a87891edbfb72ead","tid":203503,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T10:40:52.000Z","msg":"災民冇得驅散，因為冇得返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"595c6035dc3d132436afcb269543134c49939204","tid":203503,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T10:44:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>災民冇得驅散，因為冇得返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n麥當勞之家"},{"pid":"73fbea267648ff01e012ae46aedeec46dc9f0d53","tid":203503,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T10:46:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>災民冇得驅散，因為冇得返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n麥當勞之家</blockquote><br />\n叫劉華收留"},{"pid":"68065bc4de2cf0864446a31cf4789584ff1e7438","tid":203503,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T10:47:34.000Z","ms